### **5. Deployment and Monitoring**

1.  **Push to GitHub/GitLab:** Connect your Vercel project to your Git repository.
2.  **Deploy:** Every `git push` will trigger a new deployment.
3.  **Monitor Costs:** The most important part for this project.
    *   **In-App Tracker:** The `CostTracker` component gives you a real-time *estimate*.
    *   **Vercel AI Gateway Dashboard:** This is your source of truth. Go to the Gateway dashboard to see the exact, up-to-the-minute costs, token counts, and request logs for each model route. You can set up alerts if Vercel provides them or check this dashboard frequently to ensure you don't cross the $10 threshold.

This design provides a robust, scalable, and cost-aware solution for comparing AI models, built entirely on the modern Vercel and Next.js 15 stack.
